        {
            "author_association": "NONE",
            "body": "From what i understand from the above conversation this should be the plan to achieve it \n \nImplement a `:restart` command that functions as follows:\n \n 1. Save the current session state using `:mksession`.\n 2. detach all ui components using `:detach` [reference  commit](https://github.com/neovim/neovim/commit/4b0e2605eaf90268195029a29f10903dc82729e7)\n 3. The UI client stops the current `nvim --embed` server.\n 4. The UI client starts a new `nvim --embed` server and attaches to it.\n 5. Restore the saved session state.\n\nshould i open a pull request working on it ?",
